Package com.geneea.celery

Celery client and worker for connecting your JVM code with other languages.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Celery.AsyncResult<T>  
    CeleryTaskLoader
    Service (instantiated by ServiceLoader) instantiating a CeleryTask within CeleryWorker.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Celery
    A client allowing you to submit a task and get a Future describing the result.
    CeleryWorker
    CeleryWorker that listens on RabbitMQ queue and executes tasks.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    DispatchException
    An exception that occurred when trying to figure out the method that should process the task in the worker.
    UnsupportedProtocolException
    Thrown when the caller can't process the URI because it can't handle its protocol (scheme).
    WorkerException
    An exception produced by the remote worker.
  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    CeleryTask
    Marks your code as a Celery CeleryTask.

Package com.geneea.celery Description

Celery client and worker for connecting your JVM code with other languages.

For examples of usage, see http://crabhi.github.io/celery-java/.
